[ACTIVITY] 大宗電商出貨三階審核流程
[ACTOR] 賣家 -> {specs/actors/賣家.md}
[ACTOR] 營運主管 -> {specs/actors/營運主管.md}
[ACTOR] 法務 -> {specs/actors/法務.md}

[INITIAL]
[STEP:1] @賣家 {specs/commands/提交大宗出貨申請.feature}
[STEP:2] @營運主管 {specs/queries/檢核訂單金額與庫存.feature}
[DECISION:1a] 金額層級
  [BRANCH:1a:高額]
    [STEP:1a.1] @營運主管 {specs/commands/啟動高額出貨審核.feature}
    [DECISION:1a1] 商品類型
      [BRANCH:1a1:管制品]
        [STEP:1a1.1] @營運主管 {specs/commands/管制品類加強簽核.feature}
        [DECISION:1a1a] 法務複核
          [BRANCH:1a1a:需要]
            [STEP:1a1a.1] @法務 {specs/commands/法務深度審查.feature}
          [BRANCH:1a1a:免除]
            [STEP:1a1a.2] @法務 {specs/commands/備案存檔.feature}
        [MERGE:1a1a]
      [BRANCH:1a1:一般品]
        [STEP:1a1.2] @營運主管 {specs/commands/一般品類簽核.feature}
        [DECISION:1a1b] 跨境合規風險
          [BRANCH:1a1b:高風險]
            [STEP:1a1b.1] @法務 {specs/commands/跨境合規評估.feature}
          [BRANCH:1a1b:低風險]
            [STEP:1a1b.2] @法務 {specs/commands/快速核可.feature}
        [MERGE:1a1b]
    [MERGE:1a1]
  [BRANCH:1a:小額]
    [STEP:1a.2] @營運主管 {specs/commands/小額快速核可.feature}
[MERGE:1a]

[STEP:3] @賣家 {specs/ui/顯示審核結果.md}
[FINAL]
